title: "mcp-taiwan-legal-db: Taiwan Legal Database MCP Server"
message: "If you use this dataset in research, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: LawChat
    email: opensource@lawchat.com.tw
    website: https://lawchat.com.tw
repository-code: https://github.com/lawchat-oss/mcp-taiwan-legal-db
abstract: >-
  MCP server for Taiwan legal data: judicial judgments, national regulations
  (11,700+ statutes), and 868 Constitutional Court rulings (Grand Justices'
  Interpretations + Constitutional Court Judgments) with full reasoning text,
  citation graph extraction, and offline-first access.
keywords:
  - taiwan
  - legal data
  - constitutional law
  - judicial yuan
  - citation graph
  - mcp
  - traditional chinese
  - open data
